@HostAddress = http://localhost:5203

### Trigger Trace Log
GET {{HostAddress}}/log-debug
Accept: application/json

### Trigger Information Log
GET {{HostAddress}}/log-info
Accept: application/json

### Trigger Warning Log
GET {{HostAddress}}/log-warning
Accept: application/json

### Trigger Error Log
GET {{HostAddress}}/log-error
Accept: application/json

### Trigger Fatal Log
GET {{HostAddress}}/log-fatal
Accept: application/json